data.description: The special feature of this home is the enormous first floor suite added in 2005 offering a separate living room, mammoth bedroom w/walk-in closet, private bath & laundry room. The lower level has a finished recreation room, work bench & storage space. The original home has 4 bedrooms & 2.5 baths. Besides the attached 3 car garage, a second double garage is located to the west side of the lot with a separate double deep concrete drive. Parking availability is not a problem.  A gazebo rests on the concrete private patio. If living space is the need, you'll find it here!  A 33' all season room is part of the package.
